The simplest is to update to Node.js v12:

https://github.com/nodesource/distributions#readme -> owner site


https://askubuntu.com/questions/1382565/npm-does-not-support-node-js-v10-19-0/1382566#1382566
https://github.com/nodejs/help/issues/3644

curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_12.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs
